<p>So, this is the first track on the first Puddle of Mudd album that I ever heard.  My ears immediately tuned in to the full-bodied guitar/bass combination and I was, without realising it at the time, doomed to hum the main chord sequence over and over for the next 10 or so years.  It was awesome then and there has been little to surpass it ever since.</p>

