<p>I've embedded this video as an easy way of getting Control into this not-really-a-fan page, but I still haven't watched it.  I only have the vaguest idea of what the band members look like - and I really doubt that I'm missing anything.  Anyway, I don't need to see them to enjoy their music, I only need a decent pair of speakers and an empty house so I can crank them up and feel the rhythms pushing the air aside.</p>

